  "text": "In this study, several hindcasts were run starting from November 1st 1979 to 2013. Initial conditions are provided by the ERA-Interim reanalysis for the atmosphere (Dee et al., 2011) , ORA-S4 ocean reanalysis for the ocean [CITATION_1] , and outputs of a coupled model run nudged towards ERA-Interim in the atmosphere and ORA-S4 in the ocean to initialize the sea ice and land 115 surface components.",
